    %%time
attrs = ['cashflow', 'balance_sheet', 'financials']
yf_d = {}
for attr in attrs:
    df = getattr(YF_aapl, attr)
    yf_d[attr] = df.shape[0]
    %%time attrs = ['cashflow', 'balance_sheet', 'financials'] yf_d = {} for attr in attrs: df = getattr(YF_aapl, attr) yf_d[attr] = df.shape[0]

    yahooquery¶

    In [4]:
    Copied! 
    %%time
methods = ['cash_flow', 'balance_sheet', 'income_statement']
yq_d = {}
for method in methods:
    df = getattr(YQ_aapl, method)()
    df.set_index(['asOfDate', 'periodType'], inplace=True)
    df = df.T
    yq_d[method] = df.shape[0]
    %%time methods = ['cash_flow', 'balance_sheet', 'income_statement'] yq_d = {} for method in methods: df = getattr(YQ_aapl, method)() df.set_index(['asOfDate', 'periodType'], inplace=True) df = df.T yq_d[method] = df.shape[0]
    Wall time: 1.34 s
    In [5]:
    Copied! 
    # Comparison of the number of items returned for each
cash_flow = yf_d.pop('cashflow')
income_statement = yf_d.pop('financials')
yf_d.update({'cash_flow': cash_flow, 'income_statement': income_statement})
pd.DataFrame({'yahooquery': yq_d, 'yfinance': yf_d})
    # Comparison of the number of items returned for each cash_flow = yf_d.pop('cashflow') income_statement = yf_d.pop('financials') yf_d.update({'cash_flow': cash_flow, 'income_statement': income_statement}) pd.DataFrame({'yahooquery': yq_d, 'yfinance': yf_d})

dataframes = []

    options = YF_aapl.option_chain(option)

yf_option_chain = pd.concat(dataframes)
